cubescript::void_t

cubescript::void_t Struct Reference

Pseudo void type. More...

#include <cubescript.hpp>

Detailed Description

Pseudo void type.

The native void type cannot be used as a return type on functions that are accessible from CubeScript, instead use void_t.
